"title": "6647: eternal life, experience of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "6647",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Eternal life is a present possession, to to be experienced here and now, but it also offers rich and joyful future prospects.</p>\n<h2>Eternal life as a present possession</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:24\">JHN 5:24</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom6:22\">ROM 6:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal2:20\">GAL 2:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:4-Eph2:5\">EPH 2:4–2:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:13\">COL 2:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:1-Col3:4\">COL 3:1–3:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:12\">1TI 6:12</a></p>\n<h3>The Holy Spirit as a sign of new life</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:9\">ROM 8:9</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor3:16\">1CO 3:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor6:19\">1CO 6:19</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:13-Eph1:14\">EPH 1:13–1:14</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim1:14\">2TI 1:14</a></p>\n<h3>Eternal life as a future hope</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:3-1Pet1:5\">1PE 1:3–1:5</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Present experience the basis for future hope</h3>\n<p><em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:27\">COL 1:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess2:16-2Thess2:17\">2TH 2:16–2:17</a></p>\n<h3>Eternal life contrasted with present suffering</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:18\">ROM 8:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:11-Matt5:12\">MAT 5:11–5:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:28-Luke18:30\">LUK 18:28–18:30</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:29\">MAT 19:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:29-Mark10:30\">MRK 10:29–10:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:12\">JAS 1:12</a></p>\n<h3>The life to come</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim4:8\">1TI 4:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom2:7\">ROM 2:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor5:4\">2CO 5:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:5\">COL 1:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:21\">JUD 1:21</a></p>\n<h3>Being with Christ for ever</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor5:8\">2CO 5:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke23:43\">LUK 23:43</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:2-John14:3\">JHN 14:2–14:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:24\">JHN 17:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess4:15-1Thess4:17\">1TH 4:15–4:17</a></p>\n<h2>Assurance of eternal life</h2>\n<h3>The keeping power of God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:28-John10:29\">JHN 10:28–10:29</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:38-Rom8:39\">ROM 8:38–8:39</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:3-1Pet1:5\">1PE 1:3–1:5</a></p>\n<h3>The believer's confidence in God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:2-John17:3\">JHN 17:2–17:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps73:26\">PSA 73:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job19:25\">JOB 19:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John5:11-1John5:13\">1JN 5:11–5:13</a></p>\n<h3>The sure and certain hope</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus1:2\">TIT 1:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus3:5-Titus3:7\">TIT 3:5–3:7</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:10-2Pet1:11\">2PE 1:10–1:11</a></p>",
